<div class="about">
    <a class="about__logo-link" href="#/"><img class="about__logo-img" src="../../images/logos/main-logo.svg" alt=""></a>
    <div class="about__info">
        <h4>Your personal plant care helper</h4>
        <p>
            While having multiple houseplants with different needs can be confusing, simply educating yourself
            on the proper care, and things to avoid, can simplify your plant care process massively.
            And, this resource can help you do so.
        </p>
    </div>
    <a class="about__btn-start button {{#ifCond user.error '!==' ''}}hidden{{/ifCond}}" href="#/plants" title="Click here to get started!">
        Start using
    </a>

    <a class="about__btn-join button {{#ifCond user.error '===' ''}}hidden{{/ifCond}}" href="#" title="Click here to join!">
        Join
    </a>
    <a class="about__btn-login button {{#ifCond user.error '===' ''}}hidden{{/ifCond}}" href="#" title="Click here to log in!">
        Log in
    </a>

    <div class="modal">
        <div class="modal__container animate">
            <p class="modal__title">Please fill in this form to create an account</p>
            <a class="modal__tab-join" href="#" title="Click here to join!">
                Join
            </a>
            <a class="modal__tab-login" href="#" title="Click here to login!">
                Login
            </a>
            <span class="modal__close" title="Close Modal">Ã—</span>

            <form class="modal__registration" novalidate>
                <label for="user-name"><b>Username</b></label>
                <input class="modal__username field" type="text" placeholder="e.g. nina91" name="user-name" required>

                <label for="email"><b>Email</b></label>
                <input class="modal__email field" type="text" placeholder="example@gmail.com" name="email" required>

                <label for="password"><b>Password</b></label>
                <input class="modal__password field" type="password" placeholder="Enter Password" name="password" required>

                <label for="password-confirmation field"><b>Confirm Password</b></label>
                <input class="modal__confirm-password field" type="password" placeholder="Confirm Password" name="password-confirmation" required>

                <button type="submit" class="modal__btn-join-submit">Join</button>
                <button type="button" class="modal__btn-join-cancel">Cancel</button>
            </form>

            <form class="modal__authentication" novalidate>
                <label for="user-name"><b>Username</b></label>
                <input class="modal__username field" type="text" placeholder="e.g. nina91" name="user-name" required>

                <label for="password"><b>Password</b></label>
                <input class="modal__password field" type="password" placeholder="Enter Password" name="password" required>

                <button type="submit" class="modal__btn-login-submit">Login</button>

                <button type="button" class="modal__btn-login-cancel">Cancel</button>
                <span class="modal__forgot-password">Forgot <a href="#">password</a>?</span>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>